response: The rescan should begin automatically. It may take a few minutes or more to complete. If some channels don’t reappear, try repeating this process. Rescan days occur sporadically, so rescanning your TV periodically will ensure your channels are always available. If you have any more questions or would like to know exactly when rescan days will occur in your area, please visit t.v. Answers dot org!
